# ECIS Content & SEO Standards

## Brand Voice & Tone
**Voice:** Confident, precise, helpful, authoritative yet approachable
**Tone Pillars:**
- **Authoritative:** "We secure over 200 properties across the region"
- **Precise:** Specific metrics, clear processes, definitive statements
- **Trustworthy:** Professional credentials, transparent communication
- **Helpful:** Solution-focused, actionable guidance

### Voice Examples
✅ **Good:** "Our certified officers respond within 3 minutes of alarm activation"
❌ **Avoid:** "We try to get there pretty quickly when something happens"

✅ **Good:** "Request a comprehensive security assessment"
❌ **Avoid:** "Get more info about our stuff"

## Microcopy & UI Text

### Button Text (Action-Oriented)
```vue
<!-- Use verbs that indicate specific actions -->
<button>Request Patrol Coverage</button>      <!-- Not "Learn More" -->
<button>Schedule Site Assessment</button>     <!-- Not "Contact Us" -->
<button>Book Training Session</button>        <!-- Not "Get Started" -->
<button>Download Incident Report</button>     <!-- Not "Click Here" -->
<button>Speak with Security Expert</button>   <!-- Not "Chat Now" -->
```

### Form Labels & Help Text
```vue
<template>
  <!-- Clear, specific labels -->
  <label for="property-type">Property Type</label>
  <select id="property-type">
    <option value="residential">Residential Community</option>
    <option value="commercial">Commercial Property</option>
    <option value="hoa">HOA/Neighborhood</option>
