## Page Content Structure

### Headlines & Subheadlines
```vue
<template>
  <!-- H1: Clear value proposition -->
  <h1>Professional Security Services That Protect What Matters Most</h1>
  
  <!-- Supporting headline: Specific benefits -->
  <p class="subheadline">
    24/7 patrol coverage, rapid emergency response, and comprehensive 
    security solutions for residential communities and commercial properties.
  </p>
  
