</template>
```

### Service Descriptions
Follow Problem → Solution → Outcome structure:
```markdown
**Problem:** "Property crimes in residential communities increased 15% last year"
**Solution:** "Our certified patrol officers provide visible deterrence with scheduled and random patrols"
**Outcome:** "Properties under our protection see 87% fewer security incidents"
```

### Call-to-Action (CTA) Hierarchy
1. **Primary CTA:** Main conversion goal (Request Quote, Schedule Assessment)
2. **Secondary CTA:** Lower commitment (Learn More, Download Guide)
3. **Tertiary CTA:** Social proof (Read Case Studies, View Testimonials)

```vue
<template>
  <div class="cta-section">
    <!-- Primary CTA -->
    <button class="btn btn--primary btn--large">
      Get Your Free Security Assessment
    </button>
    
    <!-- Secondary CTA -->
    <button class="btn btn--secondary">
      Download Security Checklist
    </button>
    
    <!-- Tertiary CTA -->
    <a href="/case-studies" class="link-tertiary">
      See How We Protected Similar Properties →
    </a>
  </div>
</template>
```

