## Readability Guidelines

### Sentence & Paragraph Length
- **Sentences:** 15-20 words average, 25 words maximum
- **Paragraphs:** 2-3 sentences, 50-75 words
- **Reading level:** Grade 8-10 (use tools like Hemingway Editor)

### Content Formatting
```vue
<template>
  <!-- Use bullet points for features -->
  <ul>
    <li>✓ 3-minute average response time</li>
    <li>✓ GPS-tracked patrol vehicles</li>
    <li>✓ Real-time incident reporting</li>
  </ul>
  
  <!-- Use numbers and statistics -->
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-number">200+</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Properties Protected</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Emphasize key points -->
  <p>
    Our security officers are <strong>licensed and bonded</strong> with 
    <em>continuous training</em> in the latest security protocols.
  </p>
</template>
```

### Industry-Specific Terminology
**Use these terms consistently:**
- "Security patrol" (not "guard service")
- "Property protection" (not "watching stuff")
- "Incident response" (not "emergency handling")
- "Certified officers" (not "security guards")
- "Site assessment" (not "property walkthrough")

