## Content Quality Checklist
Before publishing any content:

- [ ] **Voice check:** Sounds authoritative yet approachable
- [ ] **Clarity:** Grade 8-10 reading level
- [ ] **Specificity:** Includes concrete numbers, timeframes, credentials
- [ ] **SEO:** Target keywords naturally integrated
- [ ] **Structure:** H1-H6 hierarchy logical and complete
- [ ] **CTAs:** Clear, action-oriented button text
- [ ] **Legal:** Required disclaimers and licensing info included
- [ ] **Proofread:** Grammar, spelling, and factual accuracy verified